de.wingu.sdk.utils.prerequisite

Enum Prerequisite

  • java.lang.Object
    • java.lang.Enum<Prerequisite>
      • de.wingu.sdk.utils.prerequisite.Prerequisite
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    Comparable<Prerequisite>

    public enum Prerequisite
extends Enum<Prerequisite>
    Holds all prerequisites required by SDK. Holds two types of location though SDK itself requires one of them.

    • Enum Constant Summary

      Enum Constants 
      Enum Constant and Description
      ACCESS_COARSE_LOCATION
      Corresponding to Manifest.permission.ACCESS_COARSE_LOCATION.
      ACCESS_FINE_LOCATION
      Corresponding to Manifest.permission.ACCESS_FINE_LOCATION.
      BLUETOOTH_ON
      Bluetooth is turned on in the device.
      LOCATION_SERVICES_ON
      Location turned on in the device.
      PLAY_SERVICES
      SDK requires that GooglePlayServices are available.

    • Enum Constant Detail

      • ACCESS_COARSE_LOCATION

        public static final Prerequisite ACCESS_COARSE_LOCATION
        Corresponding to Manifest.permission.ACCESS_COARSE_LOCATION. Required to make bluetooth scanning work.

      • ACCESS_FINE_LOCATION

        public static final Prerequisite ACCESS_FINE_LOCATION
        Corresponding to Manifest.permission.ACCESS_FINE_LOCATION. Required for Geofencing. It is not obligatory, but if it is not met you shouldn't use geofencing feature.

      • BLUETOOTH_ON

        public static final Prerequisite BLUETOOTH_ON
        Bluetooth is turned on in the device.

      • LOCATION_SERVICES_ON

        public static final Prerequisite LOCATION_SERVICES_ON
        Location turned on in the device.

      • PLAY_SERVICES

        public static final Prerequisite PLAY_SERVICES
        SDK requires that GooglePlayServices are available.
